PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779120674
OL,3,CDriver caught performing donuts at
OL,4,Cillegal car meet is banned from the
OL,5,Croads
OL,7,FParsons was seen accelerating
OL,8,Fextremely hard from the traffic
OL,9,Flights, causing violent wheel spin and
OL,10,Fattempting to drift, before losing
OL,11,Fcontrol while turning right onto the
OL,12,FA272 and crashing into a hedge.
OL,14,FParsons pleaded guilty to two counts
OL,15,Fof dangerous driving.
OL,17,FHe was handed a suspended sentence of
OL,18,F12 months imprisonment, disqualified
OL,19,Ffor two years and will require an
OL,20,Fextended retest before being allowed
OL,21,Fto drive again.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
