PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779120674
OL,3,CDriver caught performing donuts at
OL,4,Cillegal car meet is banned from the
OL,5,Croads
OL,7,FHe was also ordered to pay #357 costs
OL,8,Fand surcharge, and has to complete 200
OL,9,Fhours of unpaid work.
OL,11,FPolice Sergeant James Hall said: "On
OL,12,Fboth occasions his driving was
OL,13,Fdeliberate, reckless, and intended to
OL,14,Fshow off to spectators.
OL,16,F"The video of him crashing clearly
OL,17,Fshows that he lost control of the car,
OL,18,Fwhich is easily done when attempting
OL,19,Fto drive in such a dangerous manner.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
